    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >他们说，献祭她，方能拯救世界。<br>而你的选择是——拯救她，任由世界终结。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《Forbidden Offering》中违抗末日预言吧！这是一款剧情驱动的快节奏弹幕生存Rogue-lite游戏。你将扮演年轻的女巫March，为保护被视为“祭品”的女孩Lenore，杀出一条血路，直面如潮水般涌来的魔物。据说，唯有献祭Lenore，才能阻止现实世界彻底崩塌。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这趟前往Last Horizon Threshold的凶险旅途中，你们的羁绊将备受考验，而Lenore体内那股真正恐怖的力量也将逐渐揭晓。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067680/extras/92e2505981bafc6feeb7c3f511e56005.poster.avif?t=1752801456\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067680/extras/92e2505981bafc6feeb7c3f511e56005.webm?t=1752801456\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067680/extras/92e2505981bafc6feeb7c3f511e56005.mp4?t=1752801456\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>核心特色</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>毁灭性的双生法术</strong>：作为March，你将驾驭一系列独特咒语，并将其与Lenore的神秘力量相结合，创造出足以清屏的华丽连招。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>探索破碎的世界</strong>：在诡丽而独特的生态区域中穿行。每一次踏上征途，都是全新的挑战。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>进化你的力量</strong>：发掘远古遗物，解锁禁忌知识，永久强化你的能力，从一名叛逆的女巫，蜕变为末日天灾般的存在。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>混乱中铸就的羁绊</strong>：你与Lenore之间牢不可破的羁绊，是你们生存下去的关键。在激战中，她独特的援护是抵御步步紧逼的黑暗的唯一希望。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067680/extras/ddc89e2e274c3903547eb7396905dfa8.poster.avif?t=1752801456\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067680/extras/ddc89e2e274c3903547eb7396905dfa8.webm?t=1752801456\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067680/extras/ddc89e2e274c3903547eb7396905dfa8.mp4?t=1752801456\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >世界的命运在你手中，而你的抉择或许会亲手葬送一切。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >是违抗命运，拥抱终焉？还是任由黑暗，吞噬所有？</p>",
